          Finance your dream boat with 0% deposit. Fishing boats, speedboats, yachts, jet skis. New & used vessels accepted.
          <strong class="text-yellow-400">Marine specialists since 1985.</strong>
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mb-8">
          <a href="https://wa.me/60175700889?text=Hi%20I%27m%20interested%20in%20boat%20financing" class="bg-yellow-400 text-navy-900 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-yellow-300 transition">WhatsApp Us Now</a>
